{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "172e537e-6509-4aef-97e1-be89af647ec7",
    "name": "LT04: Rogues Accused",
    "sceneId": "981ec865-3e1b-4f3e-bb0d-11df2bc7d593",
    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "e6010d95-2a41-4169-8794-363c9b834730",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "1714a508-83df-4a81-a06b-eb846ce23bf2",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "d2ef4629-371f-4dd5-980d-2f4737cb27a8",
                            "text": "Ask About Thomas",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "351feea7-aca5-42b8-827b-841e87ffcaed",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "So how are things going for you?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.branch",
                                    "sections": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                                            "expression": {
                                                "type": "expressions.inTags",
                                                "scope": "actor",
                                                "scopeId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                "scopeFilterId": null,
                                                "tags": "kwirkpracticecomment",
                                                "has": true
                                            },
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "82af0d28-76b2-41d2-9325-61c63d347ef0",
                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "I've been thinking over our conversations in the Practice Room about the school thief. The whole thing sounds implausible.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "701e5b76-9080-4894-8995-f41e37b09906",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "text": "So you don't think this is some plot by Terk to kick us Rogues out of this school?",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "6bef1782-aba5-49dc-a29b-3d567cdb647f",
                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "If someone wanted to discredit Rogues, they would probably steal something valuable. Most of the items stolen were just school supplies and food items.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "acd9d59f-61fe-4f0d-8ec8-469971b261f8",
                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "I've made a list of all the items stolen from the school correlated by location and time the theft was noticed. All the things were taken sometime after curfew, probably in the early hours after midnight.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "cd26e697-53a4-426f-abb7-f6cb40968107",
                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "To capture the thief, we're going to have to sneak around in the middle of the night looking for him. He's come along our hallway several times, maybe he'll come by again.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "6c66f119-beef-45c7-a9ee-f9413f2496ed",
                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "If I could find out where he is going, then maybe I could set an ambush for him. I hope he's not dangerous when cornered.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.changeTags",
                                                    "id": "9399bbb7-8741-4d68-8c5e-42fec4fdc891",
                                                    "scope": "actor",
                                                    "scopeId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "scopeFilterId": null,
                                                    "tagsToAdd": "Library_ThieftrapComment",
                                                    "tagsToRemove": null
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "6c2a7166-47c6-4776-b5a8-17e329521296",
                            "text": "Ask About the Thefts",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e1229204-73b0-49bb-996f-5ff5b6d0f888",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "text": "So what's your theory about the thefts?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "9cdee79b-98f9-4886-ae1a-c1cded2435bf",
                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "amount": "1",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4047eff0-58ae-416d-aa58-91254032ba34",
                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "The pattern of thefts don't make a lot of sense. The stolen items are pretty random - Why steal a basket of apples, a package of paper, and a penny whistle?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "89294882-c411-41e7-ad9a-f6b6a64594c4",
                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Why not steal one of the valuable items from the Hall of Heroes? Clearly, the thief isn't stealing for the money.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3c4749df-209e-446d-b9f7-42cce54e47b2",
                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I think I need to study the castle layout more to see if there are any hidden passageways near the theft locations. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "bcc60304-5c6e-417d-8d3d-75d6823fc035",
                            "text": "Ask About Books",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4fb07e3d-bb04-482a-aaf3-5fda3c3fbe48",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "text": "Read anything interesting lately?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d2344e89-c763-40fe-9ecb-b61395d3b156",
                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I've been reading some of the old manuscripts about the history of the castle. It was built up over the years adding new levels and continually remodeling the levels.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d67197b6-490f-4f4a-b4e9-ef43685bf99f",
                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "This place must be riddled with secret areas and hidden passageways. I'm hoping to find a map or diagram so that I can locate some of the concealed corridors.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "09127a06-cff0-4f7e-b3b4-6e8b3fcf57b9",
                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Maybe then, I can track down the thief.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "5b1a50e4-903c-4867-8e66-3318b2a43cf8",
                            "text": "Compliment Thomas",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                                    "id": "c800e245-5c6f-4b7f-81bc-1200636b1c75",
                                    "options": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "a3270664-f058-4e05-b266-e20b5e93f677",
                                            "text": "Compliment His Study Habits",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "id": "bd009708-3b1c-4c38-8b93-f5f6c72e7256",
                                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                                    "target": "28",
                                                    "success": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "failure": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "e0765889-462e-4ad7-90df-11f0f13241ce",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "text": "There's no one in class that works harder than you do to learn things. It wouldn't surprise me if you wind up being the 'Rogue of the Year.'",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                    "id": "c38c4688-36e7-472b-8992-cded9ff8c4a4",
                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "amount": "2",
                                                    "change": "1",
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "9bab0104-a9c2-4f1b-a10c-e6651e3c70a6",
                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "Me? I'm not sure I can ever be good enough for that.",
                                                    "emotion": "4",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "1918d977-6e28-4ad1-8a19-8a31421c7730",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "text": "Maybe not, but it won't be from lack of trying. ",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": 0,
                                            "ExitMenu": false
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "e188fb1c-d1e5-4983-855a-5ba3eb3268d9",
                                            "text": "Say Something Sweet",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "id": "e416f58b-51a0-470a-9c76-aa48ac287f2b",
                                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                                    "target": "28",
                                                    "success": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": [
                                                            {
                                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                                "id": "46ad8624-bb38-4b95-ad5c-4de945c9777b",
                                                                "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                                "amount": "2",
                                                                "change": "1",
                                                                "notify": true
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    },
                                                    "failure": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "b961d431-1f69-4d1e-aa80-0387db4cd28e",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "text": "Did you know that your eyes sparkle when you smile? You should smile more often.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "36d4847e-6eef-40b1-82cd-454d3470049e",
                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "I... I... no, I didn't know that. I try to keep to myself here. It's easier to focus on my studies. ",
                                                    "emotion": "4",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "3",
                                            "ExitMenu": true
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "3f57da3a-c8c1-403d-aa3b-c696e5d0d67c",
                                            "text": "Ask to Get to Know Thomas Better",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "id": "f4a0e571-a0ac-4808-9c33-7d31b9046f25",
                                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                                    "target": "28",
                                                    "success": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": [
                                                            {
                                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                                "id": "ac5d4b8c-54dd-483b-9752-357e88a6c702",
                                                                "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                                "amount": "2",
                                                                "change": "1",
                                                                "notify": true
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    },
                                                    "failure": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "8a16349f-eac0-4818-b46e-0c8777cf1c17",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "text": "You know, we'd make a great team if we work together. We should take some time to get to know one another better.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "fa0d385d-7c1c-4d94-b165-fb9997d4a590",
                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "Um... uh, I prefer to work alone. I.. I'm sort of a lone wolf, bookworm person. I'm really very boring.",
                                                    "emotion": "4",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "4",
                                            "ExitMenu": true
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "b6ebb67a-f5f7-42b2-9f2f-adac84358f18",
                                            "text": "Flirt Blatantly",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "id": "814f88bc-1411-4ea1-8de4-4581ac960e88",
                                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                                    "target": "28",
                                                    "success": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "failure": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "56ecb2a0-bdd8-405a-9daf-ef3ec554a119",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "text": "Why don't you and I go off and do a little exploring on our own?",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "f14ab13c-9c0a-4ea8-b01e-8a4ca4fcbb5a",
                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "I don't think that wandering around randomly will help us find the School Thief. I'm going to focus on studying the layout of the castle and finding potential hidden passageways.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "3",
                                            "ExitMenu": true
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                                    "Unique": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "41a88243-adb2-4a6f-b815-6261b21035e7",
                            "text": "Say Goodbye",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "056729cd-2279-4860-97ce-08de3d07bcbd",
                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "amount": "1",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
